            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.1 概述"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                92,
                102,
                196,
                123
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608需要通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                139,
                138,
                905,
                175
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/df229fcb5e3b222c3e04ab69084b325f0e67f1de80f7d4e78b7826b543232f5d.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                188,
                186,
                213
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                197,
                226,
                213
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "目前，LA2608只支持与 H3C公司的无线控制器互通。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                224,
                564,
                241
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                282,
                484,
                302
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                320,
                905,
                356
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "图1 配置 LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                362,
                431,
                378
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/4ccee3c380f5b5eebb16634b6395a8bb9bfc14476278ece11f5321e85f98b226.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
